<br>
Okay - so let me pacify the GOLEM this time.  (jumping ahead past the resists)  It Sticks!  So I pull the Crusader.  GOLEM comes right along with it.<br>
<br>
If this spell was a viable option to use - then a Pally could be an alternative puller to SK or MONK.  No, we don't pull...we just sit back and let those that can do the work.  Outdoors?  Why pull, the ranger/druid will just harmony them.<br>
<br>
Ahhhh - the great noble pally - sitting around playing solatiare while others do the hard work.<br>
<br>
Any tricks for Pacify actually working?  I have buffed Charisma too in attempts of making this less resisted.<br>
<br>
(did this sound like a rant?)<br>
<br>
